Yocto layer for Xenomai Real-time support for i.MX SoCs. 

This layer implements xenomai on the following SoCs:

imx6evk or Boundary device boards like nitrogen6*.

Exemple of local.conf file :
MACHINE = "imx6qsabrelite"
PREFERRED_PROVIDER_virtual/kernel = "linux-xenomai-imx6"
PREFERRED_VERSION_xenomai = "3.0.2"
IMAGE_INSTALL_append = " xenomai"

Layer depends on other layers (branch jethro) :
git://git.yoctoproject.org/poky.git
https://github.com/Freescale/meta-fsl-arm
https://github.com/Freescale/meta-fsl-arm-extra
git://git.openembedded.org/meta-openembedded
git://git.yoctoproject.org/poky.git

